query:
SELECT id, strategySymbol, status, isTest, ipAddress, createdAt,
       SUBSTRING(payload, 1, 200) as payload_preview
FROM webhook_logs 
WHERE DATE(createdAt) = CURDATE()
ORDER BY createdAt DESC
LIMIT 30;
